 examine how long it is likely to take for a company to earn an amount equal to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1223491460/image_1223491460.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743685-how-long-will-it-take-for-dollar-general-earnings-to-pay-back-investors", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 23:43:13"}, {"id": "4743682", "title": "Investigation Into AMMO's Accounting Piles On Financial Weakness", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313319903/image_1313319903.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Modern Pistols And Gun Cartridges At Gun Training Range\" data-id=\"1313319903\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313319903/image_1313319903.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313319903/image_1313319903.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313319903/image_1313319903.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313319903/image_1313319903.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313319903/image_1313319903.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313319903/image_1313319903.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313319903/image_1313319903.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313319903/image_1313319903.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">AleksandarGeorgiev</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>AMMO, Inc. </strong>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/POWW\" title=\"AMMO, Inc.\">POWW</a></span>), the ammunition producer and operator of the GunBroker online firearms marketplace, is facing issues on several fronts. On top of weak profitability and a dramatic revenue hiccup in the company\u2019s fiscal Q1, the company is facing accounting-based</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1313319903/image_1313319903.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743682-investigation-into-ammos-accounting-piles-on-financial-weakness", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 23:38:26"}, {"id": "4743686", "title": "Inflation Still Has The Potential To Derail The Fed's Rate Plan", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157311703/image_157311703.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Inflation\" data-id=\"157311703\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3504px\" height=\"2336px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157311703/image_157311703.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157311703/image_157311703.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157311703/image_157311703.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157311703/image_157311703.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157311703/image_157311703.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157311703/image_157311703.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157311703/image_157311703.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157311703/image_157311703.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JLGutierrez</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>Earlier today, the Bureau of Labor Statistics released the <a href=\"https://www.bls.gov/news.release/cpi.nr0.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">Consumer Price Index for November</a>, which is one of the most popular measures of inflation in the economy. While the report met market expectations, and stocks have been muted in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157311703/image_157311703.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743686-inflation-still-has-the-potential-to-derail-the-feds-rate-plan", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 23:20:42"}, {"id": "4743675", "title": "Comcast: 2025 Looks Promising, But Can The Company Execute?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/530183821/image_530183821.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Comcast\" data-id=\"530183821\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5184px\" height=\"3456px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/530183821/image_530183821.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/530183821/image_530183821.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/530183821/image_530183821.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/530183821/image_530183821.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/530183821/image_530183821.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/up