ticle/4743672-panasonic-ai-and-hvac-businesses-have-favorable-prospects-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 23:00:43"}, {"id": "4743668", "title": "Toromont Industries: Paving The Way For Good Returns On The Road Ahead", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351381168/image_1351381168.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Toromont Cat sign and a Caterpillar excavator at their facility in Stoney Creek, ON, Canada.\" data-id=\"1351381168\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351381168/image_1351381168.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351381168/image_1351381168.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351381168/image_1351381168.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351381168/image_1351381168.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351381168/image_1351381168.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351381168/image_1351381168.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351381168/image_1351381168.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351381168/image_1351381168.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Please note all $ figures are in $CAD, not $USD, unless otherwise stated. </em></p> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>Toromont Industries (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">TSX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TIH:CA\" title=\"Toromont Industries Ltd.\">TIH:CA</a></span>) has been a fantastic long-term <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4659200-toromont-industries-a-worthy-addition-to-any-dividend-portfolio\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4659200-toromont-industries-a-worthy-addition-to-any-dividend-portfolio\" target=\"_blank\">compounder</a> despite its exposure to somewhat cyclical end markets in construction, mining, and forestry. As a heavy equipment dealer</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1351381168/image_1351381168.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743668-toromont-industries-paving-the-way-for-good-returns-on-the-road-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 22:51:36"}, {"id": "4743666", "title": "TopBuild: Warming Up To This Insulator Supplier", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1266869288/image_1266869288.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Mature man renovating home interior\" data-id=\"1266869288\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1266869288/image_1266869288.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1266869288/image_1266869288.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1266869288/image_1266869288.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1266869288/image_1266869288.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1266869288/image_1266869288.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1266869288/image_1266869288.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekinga